# ğŸ“Š ULTRA SYNC PERFORMANCE FIX: Performance Optimizer é…å»¶åˆæœŸåŒ–ï¼ˆloggeråˆæœŸåŒ–å¾Œï¼‰
_performance_optimizer = None
try:
    from ultra_sync_performance_optimization import UltraSyncPerformanceOptimizer, performance_timing_decorator as _performance_timing_decorator
    _performance_optimizer = UltraSyncPerformanceOptimizer()
    performance_timing_decorator = _performance_timing_decorator
    logger.info("ğŸ“Š Ultra Sync Performance Optimizer åˆæœŸåŒ–å®Œäº†")
except ImportError as e:
    logger.warning(f"âš ï¸ Ultra Sync Performance Optimizer ãŒè¦‹ã¤ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“ - åŸºæœ¬æ©Ÿèƒ½ã®ã¿å‹•ä½œ: {e}")
    _performance_optimizer = None
    # ãƒ‡ã‚³ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¿ãƒ¼ã¯ãƒ‡ãƒ•ã‚©ãƒ«ãƒˆã®ã¾ã¾ã§ä½¿ç”¨

# ğŸ›¡ï¸ ULTRA SYNC ERROR LOOP PREVENTION: ã‚¨ãƒ©ãƒ¼ãƒšãƒ¼ã‚¸ç„¡é™ãƒ«ãƒ¼ãƒ—é˜²æ­¢ã‚·ã‚¹ãƒ†ãƒ åˆæœŸåŒ–
_error_loop_prevention = None
try:
    from ultra_sync_error_loop_prevention import UltraSyncErrorLoopPrevention, get_error_loop_prevention, register_flask_error_handlers
    _error_loop_prevention = get_error_loop_prevention()
    logger.info("ğŸ›¡ï¸ Ultra Sync Error Loop Prevention System åˆæœŸåŒ–å®Œäº†")
except ImportError as e:
    logger.warning(f"âš ï¸ Ultra Sync Error Loop Prevention System ãŒè¦‹ã¤ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“: {e}")
    _error_loop_prevention = None

# Flask ã‚¢ãƒ—ãƒªã‚±ãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³åˆæœŸåŒ–
